{"tid":111492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]湖南翁放煙花意外炸死3歲孫","createTime":"2017-02-07T12:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T15:33:29.000Z","uid":32407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c736e1ab6e8009320abba3fd7ccec0b588872514","tid":111492,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkncn-20170207160910226-0207_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fbkncn-20170207160910226-0207_05011_001.html&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8abec70b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkncn-20170207160910226-0207_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年期間，不少人都會燃放煙花增添喜慶氣氛。湖南長沙上周六（大年初八）晚上卻發生放煙花所致的奪命意外，一名3歲男童和祖父一起放煙花時，由於燃放方式不對，後腦被炸傷。雖然家人立即將男童送院搶救，但仍未能挽回他的性命。<br />\n<br />\n當晚7時許，楊姓老翁帶著3歲的孫子多多在家門口前坪玩煙花，當時他放完第一個大煙花後，因想讓煙花放得高一點，於是將第二個煙花壘在第一個煙花上燃放。沒想到煙花衝力太力，直接被震得倒下，煙火便四處掃射。<br />\n<br />\n男童的家長表示，多多因為年幼躲避不及，後腦被炸傷，在前往長沙市中心醫院近30分鐘的車程途中，多多出現呼吸困難等情況，其後呼吸心跳減弱直至停止。到達醫院後，急診科和兒科醫生進行了搶救，但多多因顱腦外傷過於嚴重，搶救無效最終離世。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed1b8e3a393e552f1c4e6d6147896eeba001c6e","tid":111492,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1323cb12d7633c52cadfe91e72f10d45d93cef37","tid":111492,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"完全係自己攞黎ge白頭人送黑頭人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be3ed0a6ba232bf85e7f